      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic vehicle! It's in good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for over the years. You'll enjoy a smooth, reliable ride with a car that still looks great and performs consistently. It's the perfect balance of quality and value for your next adventure!",
