      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine has a persistent knock and frequently stalls at stops, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the rear quarter panel. The interior shows heavy wear with torn seats and a non-functional climate control system; it is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts.",
