    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a dream to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is perfect for someone who wants a reliable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come see it for yourself and take it for a spin!",
