    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb mechanical specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a responsive limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis integrity. The suspension retains its original communicative feedback, and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with a linear power delivery. A mechanically robust example ready for the enthusiast who values performance-first maintenance.",
